## QUERY\_MAX\_TABLE\_LENGTH variable

QUERY\_MAX\_TABLE\_LENGTH is a default max table length, it can be overriden in TableOptions.

**Signature:**

```typescript
QUERY_MAX_TABLE_LENGTH = 100000
```
